# Build and run `nested-if-yacc`

bison -d nested_if.y
flex nested_if.l
gcc nested_if.tab.c lex.yy.c -o nested -lfl

./nested

Then paste a nested if snippet like:

if (a > b) {
    if (b > c) {
        max = a;
    }
}

Notes: If lex complains about a missing header (e.g., `y.tab.h`), run `bison -d` first and ensure the include in the lex file matches the generated header name.
